metadata.name: War Of The Dragon
metadata.description:
This collaboration is part of our journey, I'm Syadat and Lutfi have the same interest in monsters, even though we have different styles and colors of vibes, we can mix them together and make it happen.

About the "War of the dragon", the war in here is not just about war, but about fighting your own ego, fight and push yourself to be better, one of them with doing this collaboration.
